column1: # Namespace mappings, for NS URLs found in registry documents
| 0 I won't produce anything for these (superseded versions, which aren't the target of a conversion)
| 3 Autoconverted in xschemas/, but no longer maintained
| 4 Conversion code hand-written, in code/*.xslt (converters convert to v1.0 of the corresponding RDF schema)
| 6 Actually outputs stuff in VOResource/v1.0 namespace
| 7 Mentioned, but not used, at the top level of AG registry entries
